  29:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c **** /*
  30:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  * A sample implementation of pvPortMalloc() and vPortFree() that combines
  31:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  * (coalescences) adjacent memory blocks as they are freed, and in so doing
  32:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  * limits memory fragmentation.
  33:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  *
