  73:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c **** /* MSB of the xBlockSize member of an BlockLink_t structure is used to track
  74:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  * the allocation status of a block.  When MSB of the xBlockSize member of
  75:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  * an BlockLink_t structure is set then the block belongs to the application.
