  95:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c **** /* Define the linked list structure.  This is used to link free blocks in order
  96:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  * of their memory address. */
