 105:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c **** /*
 106:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  * Inserts a block of memory that is being freed into the correct position in
 107:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  * the list of free memory blocks.  The block being freed will be merged with
 108:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  * the block in front it and/or the block behind it if the memory blocks are
 109:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/heap_4.c ****  * adjacent to each other.
